recently_added.title: Recently Added
recently_added.description: Fresh out of the oven — hot new movies and shows just for you, added weekly so check in often!

316456.title: The Spy Next Door
316456.description: A man asked to baby-sit his neighbor's children winds up having to fight off secret agents after one of the kids inadvertently downloads a secret code.

321856.title: The Blair Witch Project
321856.description: A trio of filmmakers trek to uncover an urban legend, becomes an excursion into heart-stopping terror, in the original "found footage" horror.

321857.title: Book of Shadows: Blair Witch 2
321857.description: Four fans of the original BLAIR WITCH movie descend into a nightmare of murder, madness and supernatural horror in this sequel to the horror classic.

348089.title: All Is Lost
348089.description: A sailor on a solo voyage collides with a shipping container. With his boat leaking and equipment ruined, he must face a violent storm alone.

348932.title: Escape Plan
348932.description: An incarcerated structural engineer teams up with another inmate to break out of a top-secret, high-security prison in this non-stop action-thriller.

460057.title: Marauders
460057.description: An untraceable group of elite bank robbers is chased by an FBI agent who uncovers a deeper conspiracy behind the robbery-homicides.

461203.title: Instructions Not Included
461203.description: An Acapulco playboy's life turns upside down when a former fling leaves a baby on his doorstep, and he has to raise the child on his own.

469619.title: Cheech and Chong's Next Movie
469619.description: The zany, stoner twosome return for more misadventures as Cheech loses his job, deals with an angry neighbor and tries to appeal to a sexy lady.

469694.title: The Babe
469694.description: Drinking hard and playing harder, Babe Ruth rose above his hideous childhood to dominate baseball and rescue it from the brink of extinction.

470760.title: Pride and Glory
470760.description: A New York homicide detective is assigned to investigate the precinct run by his brother and where his best friend is also a suspected corrupt cop.

472182.title: Escape From Planet Earth
472182.description: When a heroic astronaut from a blue-alien planet gets trapped on notoriously dangerous Earth, his overly-cautious brother must rescue him.

477962.title: Set It Off
477962.description: Four African-American women in Los Angeles, all in dire financial circumstances, resort to robbing banks with action-packed, tragic consequences.

512448.title: New Jack City
512448.description: Two streetwise cops embark on the riskiest mission of their careers when they go undercover to bust a ruthless drug kingpin reigning over Harlem.

517750.title: The Conjuring
517750.description: Terrifying true story of a family attacked by paranormal, hostile events in their home in 1971, a disturbance only two paranormal experts could fix.

522586.title: A Man Apart
522586.description: A DEA agent, hell-bent on vengeance after a new drug kingpin murders his wife, enlists the former cartel boss in his lawless quest for justice.

528587.title: Look Who's Talking Now
528587.description: In this third chapter of the series, it is not just the kids who are talking, when the family’s favorite canines bring love and chaos into their lives

528593.title: Look Who's Talking
528593.description: An unborn baby narrates the tale of an accountant who has an affair with a married client, then meets a cabbie, who longs to go along on her ride.

528621.title: The Craft
528621.description: The new girl at a Catholic school in L.A. meets a group of socially outcast girls who form a coven with powers that soon backfire in frightening ways.

528629.title: Look Who's Talking Too
528629.description: The hilarious antics of a family with a smart aleck baby grows with the addition of a baby sister who is equally snarky and an undercover nightmare.

528667.title: When the Bough Breaks
528667.description: The trust between a married couple and the woman carrying their child is torn when the surrogate decides she wants the husband and baby for herself.

545561.title: Orphan
545561.description: A couple mourning the loss of their unborn baby adopt a little girl, except her new mom suspects something is disturbingly wrong with the child.

551830.title: The Smurfs 2
551830.description: The Smurfs and their human pals must rescue Smurfette, who has been kidnapped by a sorcerer, because she knows a spell that can foil his evil plans.

552333.title: Daddy Day Camp
552333.description: Two dads apply their childcare magic to an underdog day camp and discover that teamwork, with a dash of craziness, makes for an unforgettable summer.

554502.title: Brooklyn's Finest
554502.description: Throughout one week, the lives of three very different New York City police officers change as a result of a violent drug operation.

555847.title: Tyler Perry's Why Did I Get Married?
555847.description: Based on Perry's popular stage play, this is the story of a group of friends on a retreat who are about to get real about the trials of married life.

556707.title: You Got Served
556707.description: A crew of street dancers who regularly win local hip-hop competitions must come together after they’re divided by a big loss to a rich suburban crew.

563038.title: Deuce Bigalow: Male Gigolo
563038.description: A professional fish tank cleaner in desperate need of cash turns to the world's oldest profession and becomes a lover for hire.

563156.title: The Great White Hype
563156.description: A boxing promoter tries to boost the marketability of his fighter by finding the only boxer to beat the champ. Problem is, he isn't a boxer anymore.

565093.title: Baggage Claim
565093.description: Paula Patton stars as flight attendant Montana Moore, who is tired of the single life, hoping to meet the perfect man before her sister’s wedding.

568896.title: Seven
568896.description: The final case for a retiring detective and his rookie partner follows a serial killer using the Bible’s seven deadly sins to target his victims.

579298.title: Tyler Perry's Madea's Witness Protection
579298.description: The law’s takedown of a Wall Street banker who ran a Ponzi scheme is nothing compared to having to live with his family in hiding at Madea’s house!

581594.title: All About the Benjamins
581594.description: A bounty hunter’s botched capture of an inmate gets them stalked by diamond thieves who know one of them has a $60-million-winning lottery ticket.

582023.title: Woo
582023.description: After a tip from a psychic friend, a single woman in Manhattan with her own unique style has a date with a shy law clerk that he will never forget.

585058.title: Paper Soldiers
585058.description: An overeager thief joins a crew of equally inefficient burglars, in this outrageous comedy which depicts the rocky life of a criminal.

586151.title: The Andromeda Strain (1971)
586151.description: Follow Michael Crichton’s intense story of a scientific team working around the clock to stop an alien germ brought back by a space probe.

589088.title: Practical Magic
589088.description: Two magical New England sisters must outwit and overcome their family curse, which dooms the men they love to die in tragic circumstances.

589111.title: The Lost Boys
589111.description: Sleep all day. Party all night. Never grow old. Never die. When a woman and her sons move to a California town, they discover the fun of vampire life.

589161.title: Class Act
589161.description: When a bookworm and a juvenile delinquent find their academic records switched on the first day of school, they use the mix-up to their advantage.

589177.title: Money Talks
589177.description: A con man, in need of protection from the cops, the mob, and his pregnant girlfriend, joins forces with a struggling TV newsman in need of a story.

589292.title: The Mask
589292.description: Jim Carrey’s superstar role as a kind and meek bank teller who gets super powers from a Nordic mask and becomes a totally s-s-s-smokin’ hero!

589380.title: Dennis the Menace
589380.description: Based on the beloved comic strip, a well-meaning but wholly destructive little boy unwittingly wreaks mayhem upon his surly next-door neighbor.

593782.title: Deep Blue Sea
593782.description: A scientist using genetically altered shark tissue to regenerate human brains fights for her life when the huge sharks breach her deep-sea station.

594095.title: Horrible Bosses
594095.description: The comedy smash about three co-workers who decide, after a lot of liquor, to get rid of their awful bosses and only manage to make things way worse.

602253.title: Jupiter Ascending
602253.description: The visionaries of ‘The Matrix’ films return with the thrilling story of a genetically engineered tracker who informs a woman of her cosmic destiny.

602506.title: Slither
602506.description: When an alien organism attacks a small town, a devoted wife must accept that her husband has transformed from the man she married.

603322.title: Waiting to Exhale
603322.description: Angela Bassett and Whitney Houston power this groundbreaking romantic comedy about four girlfriends in Phoenix waiting for honest love relationships.

608219.title: Gone in 60 Seconds
608219.description: To save his kid brother’s life from the mob, legendary retired car thief Memphis Raines will have to steal 50 cars and he has just one night to do it.

610961.title: High Crimes
610961.description: When a savvy lawyer learns her husband is roped into a possible government conspiracy, she gets help in her investigation from a veteran military attorney.

610966.title: The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen
610966.description: A team of fantastical superheroes from literary tales are assembled by a notorious adventurer in order to save the planet from annihilation.

617476.title: The Guardian
617476.description: A jaded Coast Guard trainer butts heads with an arrogant young recruit, as the two prepare for deadly missions and daunting rescues.

618279.title: Ace Ventura: When Nature Calls
618279.description: Jim Carrey returns in this hilarious sequel as Ace Ventura, back from a spiritual quest and on the case to find a rare and sacred white African bat.

618786.title: Poetic Justice
618786.description: Janet Jackson and Tupac Shakur lead this classic about a grieving poet and a postal worker on a California road trip with their chaotic best friends.

620779.title: Siberia
620779.description: After an American diamond merchant and his lover fall into a bad business deal in Russia, they must evade crossfire between the buyer and Feds.

621292.title: Black Dog
621292.description: An ex-convict truck driver with makes one last no-questions-asked trip, only to discover that his rig is stocked with assault weapons.

621640.title: Stomp the Yard: Homecoming
621640.description: A college student joins a fraternity and attempts to prove himself as a dancer in the annual step competition, but pressure weighs heavily on him.

621683.title: Ace Ventura: Pet Detective
621683.description: When the mascot for football’s Miami Dolphins is stolen, a wacky detective goes undercover, underwater, and in over his head, to get his man or beast.

621746.title: Stomp the Yard
621746.description: Amazing step dancing sequences spice up this story of a college freshman with a past trying to fit in while joining a rival fraternity out to win.

625413.title: The Scorpion King: Book of Souls
625413.description: When an evil warlord gains a sword that can steal souls, the Scorpion King and the sister of a Nubian king must find the one thing that can stop him.

625415.title: The Scorpion King 4: Quest for Power
625415.description: After the legendary Scorpion King is betrayed by a friend, he takes on an entire kingdom to prevent an evil leader from seizing an unstoppable power.

625417.title: The Scorpion King 2: Rise of a Warrior
625417.description: After an evil general murders his father, the Scorpion King descends into the underworld to face a fearsome foe and reclaim the Sword of Damocles.

625420.title: The Scorpion King 3: Battle for Redemption
625420.description: When the Scorpion King is hired to guard a beleaguered king, things are not as they seem, so it is up to him and a lady assassin to save Scandinavia.

626771.title: An Ordinary Man
626771.description: Academy Award-winner Ben Kingsley headlines this dramatic thriller as a fugitive war criminal caught in a game of wits and peril with his housekeeper.

628023.title: The Best Little Whorehouse in Texas
628023.description: This rousing musical portrays a sheriff and a madam, who band together to save the infamous Texas Chicken Ranch from a big-city TV crusader.

637111.title: ATL
637111.description: Inside an Atlanta roller rink, four hip hop-loving teens face life-changing turning points as they prepare for what comes next after high school.

638893.title: Deliver Us From Eva
638893.description: The formidable Eva Dandridge is considered an angel by her sisters, but their men think she’s a devil. Can a new suave player win her heart?

639186.title: Cheech and Chong Get Out of My Room
639186.description: Cheech and Chong ramp up the laughs as the comedy stoner legends headline a Los Angeles-based mockumentary about their daily lives.

641484.title: Brown Sugar
641484.description: A record label producer and his longtime best friend come to the discovery that they’re in love almost immediately after one of them gets engaged.

652270.title: The Goonies
652270.description: A pair of brothers hope to save their house by following a treasure map and taking their friends along on a subterranean sea adventure.

654055.title: The Jerk
654055.description: Steve Martin makes his film-starring debut in the wacky comedy hit The Jerk. From rags to riches... to rags, the laughter never stops!

655132.title: Phenomenon
655132.description: An ordinary man discovers he has been endowed with unusual powers of intelligence and perception.

657037.title: Land of the Lost
657037.description: Comedy genius Will Ferrell stars as a has-been scientist, who gets more than he bargained for, when his expedition takes a wrong turn into hilarity.

657079.title: Let's Go to Prison
657079.description: When Fate steers a career criminal’s plot for revenge off-course, he sends his intended victim’s kid to prison, and then joins him in the slammer.

658040.title: The Grudge 3
658040.description: Tortured by visions of Kayako and Toshio, sole survivor Jake is hospitalized while his doctor investigates his story—starting with his Chicago home.

662666.title: The Bye Bye Man
662666.description: Three college friends stumble upon the horrific origins of the Bye Bye Man and learn the only way to avoid his curse: Don't think it; don't say it.

664742.title: Speed
664742.description: A city bus with a bomb aboard is set to explode if it falls under 50 mph. An L.A. officer must help one of the passengers steer the bus to safety.

670407.title: The Fifth Element
670407.description: Director Luc Besson's extravagantly-styled, outrageous sci-fi tale of good against evil set in an unbelievable twenty-third century world.

672282.title: Jumanji
672282.description: Two children find and play a magical board game, releasing a man who has been trapped in it for decades and a host of wild and exotic creatures.

672284.title: Pixels
672284.description: An unlikely group of former '80s video game champions step up to save the world from an alien invasion in this visually spectacular action-adventure.

678881.title: Paul Blart: Mall Cop
678881.description: When a shopping mall is taken over by a gang of organized crooks, it's up to a mild-mannered security guard to save the day.

680736.title: Journey to the Center of the Earth
680736.description: An Icelandic expedition goes horribly wrong for a scientist and crew trapped in a cave and plunged into unimagined worlds against an erupting volcano.

680865.title: Unforgiven
680865.description: After more than a decade living in peace a former gunslinger, lured by a huge bounty, regresses into the cold-blooded killer he once was.

682066.title: Roll Bounce
682066.description: When their rink closes down, a group of teenagers from the south side of Chicago enter the roller skating contest at a ritzy rink on the north side.

682615.title: The Bourne Ultimatum
682615.description: Jason Bourne flees a new generation of skilled CIA operatives in a non-stop race around the globe while seeking the truth behind his mysterious past.

682626.title: Get Him to the Greek
682626.description: Aspiring music exec Aaron Green has just 72 hours to deliver rock legend Aldous Snow to LA, navigating a minefield of mayhem to get there.

682628.title: The Bourne Legacy
682628.description: Agent Aaron Cross uses his genetically enhanced skills to evade the CIA after Jason Bourne's actions lead to the termination of his black ops program.

684884.title: Don't Breathe
684884.description: A group of teens breaks into a blind man's home, thinking they'll get away with the perfect crime but get more than they bargained for once inside.

688268.title: The Book of Eli
688268.description: Driven by commitment and guided by a belief in something greater than himself, a warrior not by choice but necessity, does what he must to survive.

689532.title: Rebound
689532.description: Suspended by the NCAA, a hotheaded basketball coach is forced to reevaluate his life when he's forced to coach a junior high team for a season.

689543.title: Chain Reaction
689543.description: When his mentor develops a revolutionary clean fuel source, a machinist in an alternative energy lab is ensnared in a web of espionage and murder.

694227.title: The Rundown
694227.description: A wild action-adventure about a bounty hunter named Beck, who's searching for a rebellious mobster's son and a priceless treasure in the Amazon.

694396.title: It
694396.description: In the town of Derry, Maine, seven young kids band together to stop a new killing cycle of an ancient, shape-shifting predator they can only call It.

695331.title: Missing Link
695331.description: Mr. Link recruits explorer Sir Lionel Frost and adventurer Adelina Fortnight to help find his long-lost relatives in the fabled valley of Shangri-La.

695535.title: The Perfect Guy
695535.description: After a painful breakup with her long-term boyfriend, Leah jumps into a passionate relationship with a stranger who seems to be the perfect guy.

698965.title: The Jackal
698965.description: An engaging suspense thriller about a ruthless assassin hired to eliminate a powerful, high-ranking official in the U.S. government.

698980.title: Dead Silence
698980.description: After the murder of his wife, a man returns to his hometown and uncovers the terrifying legend of Mary Shaw, a cursed ventriloquist from the 40s.

705944.title: Babylon A.D.
705944.description: A ruthless mercenary is hired to smuggle a woman from the post-apocalyptic confines of Eastern Europe to the glittering megalopolis of New York City.

707321.title: 3 From Hell
707321.description: After barely surviving prison, the demented Firefly clan goes on the run and unleashes a whole new wave of murder, madness and mayhem on the innocent.

710969.title: Black and Blue
710969.description: After capturing crooked cops killing drug dealers on her body cam, a rookie must evade the narcotics officers after her incriminating evidence.

712242.title: Tough Guys Don't Dance
712242.description: When Tim Madden wakes up from a memory-erasing drinking binge, he learns that it'll take more than a day to recover after finding blood in his car.

712894.title: The Help
712894.description: In 1960s Mississippi, a Southern girl turns her small town on its ear when she interviews African-American maids who have worked for white families.

713221.title: Safe Word
713221.description: When a newlywed couple decides to open their relationship to strangers, the wife quickly realizes her husband is a sadistic monster whose fetishes might destroy her.

716385.title: Crazy/Beautiful
716385.description: Fate brings together two high school seniors from opposite sides of the track in this sexy, fun, and energetic story of first love.

716387.title: Keeping Up with the Joneses
716387.description: Go deep undercover in this comedy about a suburban couple who discovers their neighbors are covert spies embroiled in an international conspiracy.

716389.title: Poltergeist
716389.description: In this reimagining of the 1982 classic, a family fights to rescue their daughter from a demon invading their home through a portal to another world.

716834.title: The Three Stooges
716834.description: While trying to save their childhood home, knuckleheads Larry, Curly, and Moe wind up embroiled in a murder plot and stumble into roles on reality TV.

720844.title: Dead Poets Society
720844.description: John Keating, a charismatic English professor, uses poetry to breathe new life into his students at a strict, all-boys prep school.

724345.title: Identity Thief
724345.description: A hilarious blockbuster hit about an accounts representative who has one week to clear his name after a con artist steals his identity.

724349.title: The Scorpion King
724349.description: The spectacular Mummy series explodes into a new realm of non-stop action following the epic story of the most feared warrior of the ancient world.

724351.title: Death Becomes Her
724351.description: When a jealous actress discovers an immortality treatment, she decides to take advantage of it to become young again and outshine her rival.

100000001.title: Kubo and the Two Strings
100000001.description: After accidentally summoning an evil spirit, Kubo must recover his fallen samurai father’s mystical weaponry and discover his own magical powers.

100000170.title: Maze Runner: The Death Cure
100000170.description: In this epic conclusion, Thomas leads the Gladers on their final mission to break into the legendary Last City—the deadliest maze of all.

100000215.title: Man of the House
100000215.description: A hard-edged Texas Ranger is forced to go undercover as an assistant coach to protect a group of college cheerleaders after they witness a murder.

100000216.title: Oldboy
100000216.description: An advertising executive finds himself kidnapped and held hostage for 20 years in solitary confinement without any indication of his captor's motive.

100000217.title: Saving Silverman
100000217.description: It takes a woman with the looks of an angel and the demeanor of the devil to test an inseparable friendship three men have shared since grade school.

100000218.title: The Secret in Their Eyes
100000218.description: A recently retired criminal court investigator writes a novel based on a twenty-five-year-old unresolved rape and murder case, which still haunts him.

100000219.title: The Smurfs
100000219.description: When evil wizard Gargamel chases the tiny blue creatures out of their village, they tumble from their magical world into the middle of Central Park.

100000379.title: Classmates
100000379.description: A computer mixup gives two college freshman the chance to swap places but things take a turn when the switch puts them both in danger.

100000434.title: Who's the Man?
100000434.description: In this hip-hop whodunnit, Doctor Dré and Ed Lover play two barbers-turned-policemen who find themselves investigating their friend’s murder.

100000439.title: Semi-Pro
100000439.description: In 1970s Michigan, the coach of a rag-tag basketball team pulls out all the stops to get his team into the NBA before their league dissolves.

100000440.title: Gremlins 2: The New Batch
100000440.description: The gremlins are back and they’ve taken up residence in a Manhattan skyscraper. When the rules are broken, the Big Apple will never be the same.

100000441.title: Gremlins
100000441.description: Billy’s furry Christmas present comes with three simple rules: keep him away from bright lights, don’t get him wet, and never feed him after midnight.

100000580.title: Ali G Indahouse
100000580.description: Ali G, a white gangsta-rapper wannabe, gets hilariously entangled in an evil Chancellor’s plot to overthrow Great Britain’s Prime Minister.

100000585.title: Gone Before Her Time: Brittany Murphy
100000585.description: Scene-stealing starlet Brittany Murphy was destined for Hollywood’s A-list until her untimely and mysterious death turned out the lights on her lifelong dreams.

100000587.title: Fireproof
100000587.description: This story follows one man's desire to transform his life and marriage through the healing power of faith and fully embrace the fireman's code.

100000720.title: I Now Pronounce You Chuck & Larry
100000720.description: In order to receive domestic partner benefits, two straight Brooklyn firefighters are forced to improvise as love-struck newlyweds.

100000721.title: MacGruber
100000721.description: The former special forces operative and his sidekick set out on a mission to recover a stolen nuclear warhead from his sworn enemy, VonCunth.

100000722.title: Beautiful Creatures
100000722.description: Two women try to outwit the law and pull off a fake ransom scam after one of them accidentally kills the other's abusive boyfriend.

100000723.title: Altered
100000723.description: From the writer-director of The Blair Witch Project comes this story of four men who are out to get the alien life form that killed their friends.

100000724.title: Bruce Almighty
100000724.description: An encounter with God leaves a frustrated, wannabe news anchor for a Buffalo TV network with divine power and a life-altering challenge.

100000747.title: Dead Hot
100000747.description: After a ghost hunt gone wrong, students of witchcraft Vanessa Hudgens and GG Magree travel to Salem, Massachusetts to seek out proper mentorship from experts in witchcraft.

100000849.title: All Eyez on Me
100000849.description: This biopic chronicles the ascent of hip-hop legend and activist Tupac Shakur centering on the relationships and experiences that shaped his artistry.

100000850.title: Booksmart
100000850.description: About to graduate, two best friends try to cram four years of fun into one night after spending their high school years entirely focused on studying.

100000867.title: Howard the Duck
100000867.description: A fast-talking, cigar-chomping, beer-loving duck is transported to Earth from a parallel universe and must save the planet from an alien invasion.

100000868.title: Harry and the Hendersons
100000868.description: On the way home from a camping trip in the mountains, the Henderson family encounters a friendly Sasquatch and helps him evade a malicious hunter.

100000869.title: Far and Away
100000869.description: Two young Irish immigrants flee their home country on a ship bound for America, where they find love and new possibilities in its dangerous frontiers.

100000935.title: Paul
100000935.description: During a road trip to visit famous UFO sites, two sci-fi geeks encounter a wisecracking alien named Paul who is on the run from federal agents.

100000963.title: Blood, Sweat and Cheer
100000963.description: A mother seeking to relive her glory days poses as her teen daughter to join a high school dance team.

100000965.title: A Good Man
100000965.description: Struggling in the aftermath of his wife's affair, a man's attempt at a new relationship begins to spiral out of control when he notices familiar signs.

100001021.title: Foxfire Light
100001021.description: A prim and proper young woman flees the city for her uncle's mountain home and falls for a rugged local cowboy, but the pair are like oil and water.

100001048.title: Bury the Bride
100001048.description: Bride to be June’s bachelorette party turns deadly when her blood thirsty fiancé and his friends show up to crash the party.

100001214.title: Murder at the Murder Mystery Party
100001214.description: An aspiring actress thinks a murder mystery party will be the perfect way to break into the LA scene — until she realizes that the murder is real, and she’s being framed for it.

100001219.title: TMZ No BS: Cardi B
100001219.description: Stripper. Reality Star. Rap Legend. Cardi B became an undeniably talented and entertaining celebrity, but with her rise came headlines, cheating scandals, court cases, and beefs.

100001250.title: Marry F*** Kill
100001250.description: After their friend Beth’s suicide, five estranged friends learn Beth bequeathed them her ancestral home - but unbeknownst to them, they’ve inherited something far more sinister.

100001394.title: Carnifex
100001394.description: On their quest into the Australian Outback to track the animals left displaced by bushfires, a trio discovers a terrifying species and realize they're the ones being tracked.

100001401.title: No Way Out
100001401.description: Forced to take on a double murder case after the suspect threatens his family, attorney Brian Nelson begins to unravel the facts and learns the case isn’t what it seems.

100001403.title: Snow Dogs
100001403.description: When Miami dentist Ted Brooks inherits a team of rambunctious sled dogs, he has to learn the trade or lose his pack to a crusty mountain man.

100001475.title: Doctor Dolittle
100001475.description: A workaholic doctor disrupts his family life and raises the concerns of his colleagues when he rediscovers his ability to communicate with animals.

100001476.title: RocketMan
100001476.description: An accident-prone computer programmer’s childhood dream comes true when he’s selected by NASA to join the first manned mission to Mars.

100001495.title: Eight Below
100001495.description: Stranded in Antarctica due to an unforgiving winter storm, a team of sled dogs must survive together until their determined trainer can rescue them.

100001591.title: Space Jam: A New Legacy
100001591.description: When a rogue artificial intelligence kidnaps his son, LeBron James recruits the Looney Tunes to face off against the Goons in a game of basketball.

100001592.title: Tom & Jerry: The Movie
100001592.description: A desperate event planner conspires with Tom to catch his nemesis Jerry as the mouse wreaks havoc throughout a fancy Manhattan hotel during a wedding.

100001593.title: Shaft
100001593.description: After his friend’s untimely death, cyber security expert John Shaft Jr. teams up with his estranged father to search the city’s criminal underbelly.

100001594.title: Rampage
100001594.description: When a group of animals becomes vicious after a genetic experiment goes awry, a primatologist must find an antidote to avert a global catastrophe.

100001596.title: Mortal Kombat
100001596.description: An MMA fighter with a mysterious dragon birthmark learns that he’s been chosen to fight for Earthrealm in the final battle against the evil Outworld.

100001597.title: It: Chapter Two
100001597.description: When Pennywise resurfaces after 27 years, the Losers Club reunites to prevent another reign of terror and defeat It once and for all.

100001598.title: The Conjuring: The Devil Made Me Do It
100001598.description: Paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren uncover an occult conspiracy as they help a defendant argue that a demon forced him to commit murder.

100001600.title: Crazy Rich Asians
100001600.description: Rachel travels with her boyfriend Nick to a wedding in Singapore, where she finds out his family is extremely wealthy and not very eager to meet her.

100001602.title: Godzilla
100001602.description: A mysterious creature causes a meltdown at a nuclear power plant. Years later, the monster goes on a rampage that can only be stopped by Godzilla.
